		  <li><font color="lightblue"><b>Compact</b></font> is an urban friendly adaptation of Simple. It comes with in-built composting and allows one to reuse the water used. </li>
		  <li><font color="orange"><b>Grand</b></font> is same as Compact, but Bigger! The same hexagonal</li>
